    text: "Whoever behaves in a particularly brazen and rude manner in a public place, insulting citizens or disturbing their peace, shall be punished for the offense with a fine ranging from 700.00 to 4000.00 euros or with imprisonment for up to 30 days. JUDICIAL PRACTICE: Decision of the Constitutional Court.",
