    text: "There is no offense if the act defined as an offense was committed in necessary defense. Necessary defense is that defense which is absolutely necessary for the perpetrator to repel an immediate unlawful attack on their own or another's property. A perpetrator who exceeds the limits of necessary defense may be punished less severely. If this exceeding was done under particularly mitigating circumstances, the perpetrator may be exempted from punishment.",
    source_url: "https://www.paragraf.ba/propisi/republika-srpska/zakon-o-prekrsajima.html",
