    text: "This law regulates the conditions for prescribing offenses and misdemeanor sanctions, misdemeanor liability, misdemeanor proceedings, and the execution of misdemeanor sanctions.",
    source_url: "https://www.paragraf.me/propisi-crnegore/zakon-o-prekrsajima.html",
