      "Za prekršaj propisan zakonima ili drugim propisima Crne Gore kazniće se učinilac ako je prekršaj učinjen na teritoriji Crne Gore ili ako je učinjen na domaćem brodu ili vazduhoplovu dok se nalazi van teritorije Crne Gore.",
    text: "For an offense provided for by the laws or other regulations of Montenegro, the perpetrator shall be punished if the offense was committed in Montenegro or on a domestic ship or aircraft while outside the territory of Montenegro.",
