    law_name_local: "Zakon o prekršajima Crne Gore",
    law_category: "misdemeanor",
    article_num: "50",
    text_local:
      "(1) Niko ne može zadržati imovinsku korist pribavljenu izvršenjem prekršaja.\n(2) Korist iz stava 1 ovog člana oduzeće se, pod uslovima propisanim ovim zakonom, sudskom odlukom kojom je utvrđeno izvršenje prekršaja.",
    text: "(1) No one may retain a property benefit obtained by committing an offense.\n(2) The benefit referred to in paragraph 1 of this article shall be confiscated, under the conditions laid down in this law, by a court decision establishing that an offense was committed.",
    source_url: "https://www.paragraf.me/propisi-crnegore/zakon-o-prekrsajima.html",
