      "(1) Za prekršek je odgovoren storilec, ki je storil prekršek iz malomarnosti ali z naklepom.\n(2) Predpis o prekršku lahko določi, da je storilec odgovoren samo, če je prekršek storil z naklepom.",
    text: "(1) The offender who committed the misdemeanor through negligence or intent is liable for the misdemeanor.\n(2) A regulation on a misdemeanor may provide that the offender is liable only if the misdemeanor was committed intentionally.",
